{"tid":1328754,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[你問我答] 獨遊印度一個月平安歸來","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:56:21.000Z","uid":282482,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"23fa9ffac903cbf1e72f985d26cac5e0c6c391e4","tid":1328754,"uid":282482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"去左瑞詩凱詩同新德里，無穿無爛。<br />\n睇下大家想知啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a6ce0ae1f88891c224aab1b9fe7aa5253b0463","tid":1328754,"uid":67876,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"有無係印度宣揚反送中？"},{"pid":"6d45fb3d074a54d596796bdf718856d04f6ab1ff","tid":1328754,"uid":282482,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"d3a6ce0ae1f88891c224aab1b9fe7aa5253b0463","tid":1328754,"uid":67876,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"有無係印度宣揚反送中？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"感動mode 好多外國人都好關注，但發現唔少外國人都唔知香港同中國之間有一國兩制，所以唔係好明發生咩事。我大概每轉一個住宿就同個到啲人解釋一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889fbe88ccf5304805c817b187ae9ae4e982d5bb","tid":1328754,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:31:58.000Z","msg":"最深刻係咩<br />\n住邊"},{"pid":"1877c85b52ee858cf1f6fbf3719353684c8dafc5","tid":1328754,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"有咩地方又乾淨又有好野食？<br />\n一般人budget"},{"pid":"8114fbc953009ff22e96c6778e2c9d004e03a30b","tid":1328754,"uid":282482,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"889fbe88ccf5304805c817b187ae9ae4e982d5bb","tid":1328754,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:31:58.000Z","msg":"最深刻係咩<br />\n住邊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:49:53.000Z","msg":"最深刻係變左明星咁，<br />\n可能印度人好少見到外國旅客，<br />\n每日落村都有5-6個人想同你合照。<br />\n<br />\n試過最癲係有個女人叫我抱住佢個仔同佢地影全家幅，<br />\n個仔喊哂勁唔情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但女人好堅持<br />\n<br />\n重點當時仲係恆河條橋上面，<br />\n橋上有電單車，牛，馬嬲同人逼埋一齊，<br />\n然後我地塞住左條橋，條搖搖欲墜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n▪住宿方面▪<br />\n<br />\n瑞詩凱詩:Trinetra<br />\n<br />\n超強wifi，睇片勁順 (如果無停電)<br />\n有露台同靚景，但無冷氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3wTSmHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3wTSmHC.jpg&h=7dee9eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但廁所無抽氣扇，潮濕，無廁紙，同昆蟲同住，有潔癖可以88<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mn5tEuj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmn5tEuj.jpg&h=db710b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n＊行1分鐘就落到去村野食加買野😎好方便<br />\n<br />\n德里: <br />\n<br />\n我住左兩個地方<br />\n1. Aashianaa Gracious Living<br />\n十分推薦😂7分鐘路程到Metro,<br />\n位置好安全，因為要入兩個閘。<br />\n超強wifi，玩pubg同睇戲都唔lag,<br />\n有冷氣，一間房雙人床有四個衣櫃比你放野<br />\n乾淨企理，廁所有抽氣扇加大風扇係天花板。<br />\n有電視但唔會睇因為睇唔明😂<br />\n包早餐，係西瓜，吐司同奄列😊<br />\n1500Rupees 即係170蚊晚左右!<br />\n<br />\n2. Aero Indus Hotel<br />\n唸住方便去機場就簡左住一晚呢到<br />\n都幾後悔，首先個區域空氣勁污糟，<br />\n一般望街係灰色嘅，有車駛過仲黑色添<br />\n所以最後一日我係好唔願意出街😂<br />\n同埋床單同枕頭單都有血漬，<br />\n有冷氣同風扇，但無被。<br />\n廁所就還好，一樣無抽氣扇但係空間大啲。<br />\n但個host就好加分，流利英文可以溝通到，<br />\n好關心你需要，好肯幫你同解答你問題。<br />\n<br />\n打左好多字添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我真係好想happy share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a166822d1c412c35c5fe2eae5610c675a78c9a3a","tid":1328754,"uid":11469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"識得分yes 同no 既搖頭未"},{"pid":"3dd1511b46775c40d7e1908e3aaf1894073579ce","tid":1328754,"uid":257422,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:00:45.000Z","msg":"突發！！！！ ]  荷蘭首都大學、意大利米蘭街頭 分別驚見 林鄭壽終正寢 街招！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329216</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://na.cx/i/nNQk9Fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnNQk9Fe.jpg&h=5971b37f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67260952_2334870509933092_2471868942885322752_n.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkOaykJcWH9Wa5gUItjj08X6dcp8r3HK5_qNCEeSXnxjg_dHKav3hwm2FiACInNlK8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg8-1.fna&amp;oh=a1c45d97e8e22774df7d25b943c4a7dc&amp;oe=5DECEFD7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg8-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67260952_2334870509933092_2471868942885322752_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkOaykJcWH9Wa5gUItjj08X6dcp8r3HK5_qNCEeSXnxjg_dHKav3hwm2FiACInNlK8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg8-1.fna%26oh%3Da1c45d97e8e22774df7d25b943c4a7dc%26oe%3D5DECEFD7&h=56d1a4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/1080/https://serving.photos.photobox.com/928067831b471809fec84560cf12f81a4d43a939e63327e60d44b8c434697b1bd6e14a35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F1080%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fserving.photos.photobox.com%2F928067831b471809fec84560cf12f81a4d43a939e63327e60d44b8c434697b1bd6e14a35.jpg&h=23c7c688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">海外手足 / 準備去旅行既 print定幫手貼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c432c8cb4bc9cdb28f40cd746d4d59653176bc7f","tid":1328754,"uid":282482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1877c85b52ee858cf1f6fbf3719353684c8dafc5","tid":1328754,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:35:26.000Z","msg":"有咩地方又乾淨又有好野食？<br />\n一般人budget"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:06:40.000Z","msg":"你有冇話住邊到？<br />\n我經驗係 瑞詩凱詩係好難食到貴野&hellip;<br />\n一餐最貴係30蚊港紙加左野飲，最平6蚊港紙<br />\n<br />\n我住個區 推薦餐廳如下<br />\n全部有靚景<br />\n▪Pumpernickel German Bakery &amp; Babylon Restaurant<br />\nChocolate Brownies &nbsp;<br />\nPotatos Cheese Burger<br />\nVegan Burger<br />\n<br />\n▪Royal Cafe<br />\n Smoothie Bowl, Orange juice<br />\n<br />\n▪Sunset Cafe<br />\n所有Pasta<br />\nRoasted Potato with Cheese<br />\n<br />\n其實最抵食係街邊店<br />\n50Rupees一個包漢堡，100Rupees有Falafel 勁好食，真是不得了😂<br />\n<br />\n至於德里，物價即刻上漲百倍，<br />\n啲野食價錢同香港差唔多，<br />\n試過最抵最好食係Big Yellow Door<br />\nMetro站Central Secretariat <br />\n個到附近都多餐廳簡 <br />\n<br />\n有時我覺得太貴就食subway<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5366eb063fd3316947b1c214633ee056a83e0d06","tid":1328754,"uid":282482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a166822d1c412c35c5fe2eae5610c675a78c9a3a","tid":1328754,"uid":11469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"識得分yes 同no 既搖頭未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NifEMrc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNifEMrc.gif&h=b42dfb09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Y E S<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a11c0a4a20eda8f64aca0c9c7ac59d8a5874ac7","tid":1328754,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c432c8cb4bc9cdb28f40cd746d4d59653176bc7f","tid":1328754,"uid":282482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1877c85b52ee858cf1f6fbf371935